@startuml sequence_diagram_index
title Sequence Diagram Index

skinparam shadowing false

actor "Reviewer / Developer" as User
collections "Sequence Diagram Modules" as Modules

User -> Modules: Render 01-auth-project-dashboard-sequence.puml
User -> Modules: Render 02-project-registration-sequence.puml
User -> Modules: Render 03-start-training-job-sequence.puml
User -> Modules: Render 04-docker-log-progress-sequence.puml
User -> Modules: Render 05-artifact-notification-sequence.puml
User -> Modules: Render 06-cancel-retry-recovery-sequence.puml

note right of Modules
  Each module is a standalone PlantUML file.
  Render individual files from the diagrams/ folder.
end note

@enduml
